<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Ride Along</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset some default styles */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #18b490;
        }

        /* Wrapper for the content */
        .wrapper {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color:#183658;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header styles */
        header {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            color: #E25A44;
        }

        /* Main content styles */
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Button styles */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #E25A44;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #42b300;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="background-color: #183658;">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome to RIDE ALONG! ðŸ¥³ ðŸ¥³</h1>
        </header>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name%>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing to commute with us.</p>
            <p>Explore our website and discover interesting people that share a destination.</p>
            <p>Click the button below to get started:</p>
            <a href="[AppLink]" class="button">Explore Now</a>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br> The Ride Along Team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
